reviewText:
This kind of film appeals to a select few people: fans of the Subaru WRX, fans of the Isle of Man TT, or both, like me. The film is a
series of laps over the course in the WRX, narrated by the driver, Mark Higgins. It's fascinating stuff if you're into racing, dead boring
if you're not. If you're looking to take a different view of the Isle of Man course to what you usually see in the TT reviews, check it out.
